### 1. 平台管理员审核服务商变更（通过）
PUT http://localhost:8082/draft/1/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conclusion": 1,
  "opinion": "审核通过，服务商资质符合要求"
}

### 2. 平台管理员审核服务商变更（拒绝）
PUT http://localhost:8082/draft/2/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conclusion": 0,
  "opinion": "审核拒绝，服务商资质不符合要求"
}

### 3. 测试状态校验 - 只有待审核状态才能审核
PUT http://localhost:8082/draft/3/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conclusion": 1,
  "opinion": "测试已审核状态"
}

### 4. 服务商接受服务单（上门维修）- 多态
PUT http://localhost:8082/serviceprovider/1/serviceorders/1/accept

### 5. 服务商接受服务单（寄修）- 多态
PUT http://localhost:8082/serviceprovider/2/serviceorders/2/accept

### 6. 服务商取消服务单（上门维修）- 多态
DELETE http://localhost:8082/serviceprovider/1/serviceorders/3/cancel

### 7. 服务商取消服务单（寄修）- 多态
DELETE http://localhost:8082/serviceprovider/2/serviceorders/4/cancel

